"name": "5V 10mA LED Constant-Current Driver",
"description": "Reusable constant-current LED driver block using a TLVH431B low-voltage shunt reference, an NPN transistor, and a sense resistor. With a 5.0 V input and sufficient compliance voltage, the block regulates approximately 10 mA through the internal LED load by maintaining about 1.24 V across the sense resistor.",
